info.title: Histori Archival Node's Ethereum JSON-RPC Methods
info.description: This reference showcases an Ethereum type JSON-RPC API connecting to an Ethereum network node. Some methods require parameters, and a sample request body is presented in each method. You can copy an paste those sample requests for simplicity.
